social_posts.post_text: Bunch of Whackadoo pups. #bluey
It’s time for Blue-Topia!  Happy New Year, Gazelle is here to keep your tail shaking! #zootopia
Been working up  a whole bunch of sketch covers for a retail client! Here’s a sample. (Yes I SOMETIMES draw dudes whoa!) #harleyquinn #dcau
Felt like drawing the Plumber and the Princess! 🍄#mario #princesspeach #nintendo

Let’s look at some ART, whaddya say? Gonna start digging into the toy archive! These are some early Hasbro Princess Little Kingdom designs for Elsa. They told me to try different fashions and I… went a little nuts lol. (Hasbro no longer have the Disney princess license so it’s probably safe to share anything more than 5 years old now lol. Hey Mattel, I’m available! 🤙me!) #disneyprincess #frozen #elsa #hasbro #toystagram

When I was approached by Hasbro (specifically the wonderful @lego6398 ) to develop the Princess Comic action figs, we envisioned a MASSIVE line, including con exclusives, once Target had completed their year-long exclusive run. Unfortunately, for reasons I don’t know, retailers just weren’t interested. Which is a shame cuz we had SO many planned and Hasbro’s sculptors and painters did a fantastic job capturing my poses & expressions. Here are just a few of the year 2 figs we came up with. Maybe these gals were better suited to more of a collector licensee like Beast Kingdom, RockCandy or Super7 than straight up kids toys. Ah welp. #disneyprincess #hasbro #toystagram
I haven’t drawn my girl in a while, I’ve missed it ☺️ Just a Photoshop sketch, didn’t want to overwork it too much. #frozen #elsa

Some more Princess action fig concepts. This would be the first stage we began at, me just sketching up a bunch of fun attitudes that might make an entertaining action fig. The idea at the start was that each fig would come with an animal sidekick or a small prop but things ALWAYS get changed in order to bring a toy’s production costs  in under the set price point. (Molds are EXPENSIVE, folks…). But this is why I get hired. When you hire me, you’re essentially hiring a cartoonist with a background in animation. So I can do engaging concept drawings AND turnarounds/input! Haha. #disneyprincess #hasbro #toystagram

Most of my work in toys is in ‘small doll’ development aka action figures or other hard material figs and play sets. This was one instance where I was asked to come up with some soft doll ideas themed to Ariel. My lifelong artsy-craftsy brain went to town!  This was so fun and I’d love to do more along with fashion doll stuff. Fun fact: this work prompted me to go and buy my own sewing machine, in case I ever thought of fabricating them myself as proof of concept. I didn’t, but I DID latch onto dress making very quickly and have never looked back! (See: @amystitchesstuff ) #toystagram #ariel #hasbro

Todays #toystagram concept art is this little nugget which I forgot I did lol. Some possible adaptations of live-action Aladdin to more animation-style figs. Note that Rajah didn’t change at all 😄 Me, I was mostly like ‘ooooh, I get to see secret screen caps of the costumes yessss…’ #aladdin #hasbro #disneyprincess

My first gig at Hasbro was developing the Equestria Girls figs! We gotta lot of mileage out of these cuties and they were a LOT of fun to design. This was one of the later waves, the Mall series. The idea was that all the characters had mall jobs so I had a blast coming up with the ideas and outfits. Second pic is some of the finished figures! #mylittlepony #mlp #equestriagirls #equestriagirlsminis #toystagram #hasbro

It doesn’t happen often, but OCCASIONALLY I have to break out the Illustrator for vector art! I’m not an expert vector artist by any means, but I scraped enough knowledge over the years to make some EG illos. I have no idea if these were ever used, but even though they’re laborious, I’m still pretty proud of how they came out and how I got all the details down! (I didn’t come up with the outfits, just the poses!) #equestriagirls #hasbro #vectorart #toystagram #mlp
Cool down shake-it-off sketches playing with limited palettes. #disneyprincess #encanto #mirabelmadrigal #snowwhite #ariel #thelittlemermaid

Today’s #toystagram concept work is plucked again from the HUGE #equestriagirlsminis concept art pile. I don’t think this one made it to production but it was fun letting Dashie get her inner Guy Fieri on. All I have to say is that I am exceedingly proud of the apron designs, thank you. (Some of them were meant to go with Pinkie Pie, hence the SUGAR) #mlp #hasbro
Concept #equestriagirlsminis  sketches. IfANY character needed a peg stand, it was Sunset Shimmer 🔥 #mlp #toystagram #hasbro

Okay so y’all CLEARLY just want the Disney stuff I see how it is😜. Back to MY fave IP with some Princess Littlw Kingdom concepts for costumes. I’m particularly proud of the Sven outfit for Anna and the ‘ice cream shop’ outfit for Elsa (it was for a market playset. Yeah none of it is canon but I still go HARD on making it ‘fit’ into the frozen world) #hasbro #frozen

The last wave I did on #equestriagirlsminis was also probably the most fun: THEME PARKS! Everyone works at an Equestria theme park and my Disneyland/Knott’sberry Farm nerd went. To. Town. (Seriously, how cute is Fluttershy as an animal wrangler/jungle skipper? #toystagram #hasbro

Another batch of #disneyprincess Little Kingdom #Frozen concepts. Again, fashion doll people…call me. I love  designing pretty things, especially when they involve my fave characters. #toystagram #hasbro
#equestriagirls ‘Dance magic’ vector art. I didn’t design the fashions (lolol this is SO not my vibe!), I just did the illos. Fashion doll shoes go A BIT NUTS these days lol #toystagram #hasbro #mlp
More abandoned Hasbro Little Kingdom concepts, based on Frozen artwork by @britsketch. #hasbro #frozen
Spider-Sisters! do I want to make these? Oh heck yeah🤩. Do I have time? …no 😞#spiderman #acrossthespiderverse #frozen #frozen 2

Now available at @boxlunchgifts ! New mini backpack & passcase with my Princess @officialdisneycomics art on them! SO MUCH EXCITE! You have no idea how much I LOVE seeing my stuff on merch. (photos 3 & 4 by @teatraybat, thank you Kit!!❤️❤️) #boxlunch #disneyprincess #disneycomicprincess
More #bluey sketches! As a proud New South Welshman, I’m with Janelle. #blues #stateoforigin

Happy #worldprincessweek. Comfy Squad dance party at @spotify  #disneyprincess #frozen #comfysquad (based on a throwaway line in an earlier draft of Ralph Breaks the Internet. Shame it was dropped, IMAGINE THE CLOSING CREDITS with THIS going on!! 🤩🤩(no reposting please, share using the paper aero plane button!!)

Don’t Touch my Stuff!  Just a pic I did which I then converted to cross stitch just to see how it would work out. It came out okay but if I were to do this again I’d probably make it bigger: cross-stitch works like pixel art, the bigger the canvas the more you can refine details. Experimentation!! #worldprincessweek #disneyprincess #crossstitchersofinstagram
Wouldn’t be #worldprincessweek without my fave sisters. Hand-painted double-side ornament. Blank probably from Michael’s! #frozen #frozenfever
Just a doodle of a cute witch on her feather duster. #procreate #halloween #pinup

Very cool news: @fantagraphics published a book on the history of @officialdisneycomics and Princess comics got a shoutout, with strips by me and @askmaridee getting special mention! It also includes a Darkwing comic by @silvaniart and @tadstones! A Target exclusive book, so go getcher self one while you’re picking up underwear and maybe a new eyeliner! #disneycomics #darkwingduck #disneyprincesses (NB: in the Tiana strip, MY script had Naveen saying ‘because my waitress is a genius’.. cuz that’s their cute in-joke pet name for her (as CLEARLY seen in the movie). SOMEONE along the line changed it without telling me. Hate it when that happens 😤)

Hello! Happy to share that FINALLY I have some time to add fresh colour commission slots to my store! Colour pieces are 6x8 and come in Copic and Watercolour options ($20 extra). Ships to US and Canada only (sorry 😥). Go to my linktree in bio and click on Store, then Custom Art for full details, ordering and pricing :) #commissions #encanto #barbie #barbieandtherockers #thesoundofmusic #marvel
#doctorstrange #hauntedmansion #madameleota

Warmin’ up the ol’ sketch card muscles, cuz I’m a’coming to @emeraldcitycomiccon 2024! Feb 29-Mar 3rd! Also, here is Amy’s first Asha 😊(have not seen the movie yet, so no opinion yet, I just think she’s cute :))
#disneywish #tangled #rapunzel #disneyprincess

Happy 10th Anniversary to my favourite Disney world, FROZEN! I tried to make an art dump but I couldn’t find anything you all haven’t already seen lol . I love Arendelle and its characters so much, especially precious messy eldest child Doing Her Best, my girl ELSA. I adore her so much she’s become my default aesthetic haha. So here’s testament to the movie that inspired me to start cosplaying. Luckily I had the perfect Anna waiting to join in with @scjacka (and @cegoodman2 as Kristoff when we can coax him!) (All costumes by me, check out @amystitchesstuff for more photos . 80’s Elsa earrings by @r_janiceorlando) #frozen #cosplay #frozencosplay #anna #elsa #disneyprincess
